  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968020/extras/fa862fbe5a08a67e9a49742b536f47b5.avif?t=1730797567\" width=600 height=132 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968020/extras/ebb4296eb983fefe2b9e966a82da42bb.webp?t=1730797567\" width=600 height=39 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is a string of high-profile and gruesome murders in the city, and the killer has yet to be caught.  You are a police officer trying to find out who is behind the most high-profile murders in the city and have therefore become the number one target for a maniac! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968020/extras/900470e69bce7e233615ae6b6ff8623d.poster.avif?t=1730797567\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968020/extras/900470e69bce7e233615ae6b6ff8623d.webm?t=1730797567\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968020/extras/900470e69bce7e233615ae6b6ff8623d.mp4?t=1730797567\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968020/extras/1eba4eb5bdc8acc0ca89f24936f24b72.webp?t=1730797567\" width=600 height=39 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will encounter many challenging and unique puzzles along the way, solve them to move further towards your goal! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968020/extras/3262dc5d6c021d6073fcb8849b671dcb.poster.avif?t=1730797567\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968020/extras/3262dc5d6c021d6073fcb8849b671dcb.webm?t=1730797567\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968020/extras/3262dc5d6c021d6073fcb8849b671dcb.mp4?t=1730797567\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968020/extras/102eea15804f949ddfa23792b81a1966.webp?t=1730797567\" width=600 height=39 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready for a tense first-person psychological horror where every step could be your last, and every twist and turn could lead to new nightmarish discoveries. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968020/extras/abc9df9903a5f916bbba65f909bcde9a.poster.avif?t=1730797567\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968020/extras/abc9df9903a5f916bbba65f909bcde9a.webm?t=1730797567\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968020/extras/abc9df9903a5f916bbba65f909bcde9a.mp4?t=1730797567\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968020/extras/fa862fbe5a08a67e9a49742b536f47b5.avif?t=1730797567\" width=600 height=132 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968020/extras/ebb4296eb983fefe2b9e966a82da42bb.webp?t=1730797567\" width=600 height=39 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is a string of high-profile and gruesome murders in the city, and the killer has yet to be caught.  You are a police officer trying to find out who is behind the most high-profile murders in the city and have therefore become the number one target for a maniac! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968020/extras/900470e69bce7e233615ae6b6ff8623d.poster.avif?t=1730797567\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968020/extras/900470e69bce7e233615ae6b6ff8623d.webm?t=1730797567\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968020/extras/900470e69bce7e233615ae6b6ff8623d.mp4?t=1730797567\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968020/extras/1eba4eb5bdc8acc0ca89f24936f24b72.webp?t=1730797567\" width=600 height=39 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will encounter many challenging and unique puzzles along the way, solve them to move further towards your goal! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop plays